FreeRunner Rotate
Author:  Rui Miguel Silva Seabra <rms@1407.org>
License: GPLv3+.
Description: Inspired upon Chris Ball <cjb@laptop.org>'s previous
	     incarnation of rotate, this is a rewritten-from-scratch
	     new software that does some simple actions according to
	     the position detected by the FreeRunner's accelerometers.


######################
# How to make it run #
######################

1. Just start your phone
2. If it dies for some reason (like, currently, suspending), click on the nifty icon
